seo: 致远 OA, fileUpload.do, 前台文件上传绕过漏洞, 漏洞检测
seo_en: ZY OA, fileUpload.do, front-end file upload bypass vulnerability, vulnerability detection
summary: 该插件用于检测致远 OA 系统中 fileUpload.do 接口的前台文件上传绕过漏洞，通过构造特定请求尝试上传恶意文件并验证是否存在漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the front-end file upload bypass vulnerability in the fileUpload.do interface of ZY OA system. It constructs specific requests to attempt uploading malicious files and verifies the existence of vulnerabilities.
